pan></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/skYFhlh.png" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/xD5IFkY.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/8q2DjJb.png" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/D8W1xcv.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/IFuWOPD.png" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/W52ISX3.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Spoilers!</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/OenD8aK.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/yPqkLDh.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/99QlcdD.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/fSmEopF.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>It's a difficult duty, but on behalf of everyone who can't do it, I promise to vibe, chill, and do the fun things you don't have time for.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/Uqlmhgo.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/dAse8pj.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>I don't have a cat and my dog died back in 2023, so this is the closest you get to a cat or dog tax. Hope you had fun along the way and have a great weekend.</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/0F7D2BA</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[PoliticalWanderer]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Seems ALL his kids hate him</title><link