Den was driving.

He was our comrade, our warrior, and our beloved legendary M113 driver.

Den was the one who carried the wounded out in that M113 when others refused the task. Night after night, he drove routes of unspeakable risk.

He knew exactly what the risk was every time that engine started.

He went anyway, because someone out there needed to be brought home alive. Supplies needed to be delivered. The work had to be done.

On that night the drones kept coming. The vehicle was hit again and again. Den did not survive.

War has a way of taking people who should have had decades left to live. Den should still be here.

Instead we are left with the silence that follows a loss like this.

I keep thinking about the simple truth that behind every evacuation vehicle, every mission, every report written after the fact, there is a person inside who chose to go.

Den chose to go.

He will be missed far more than words can properly say.

Rest easy, Den. We will carry your memory with us.

Source:  https://x.com/bekamaciorowski/status/2029892635192639981 
Also on ig: https://www.instagram.com/bekamaciorowskiii/</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/P3lqfzJ</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[vladrichdemaclant]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Poverty exists because nothing satisfies the rich</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/sT0nMXH</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/JnsKpSu.png" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/sT0nMXH</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[GullahGullahIslander]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Lmao</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/u3EFQJr</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/UQXbpTv.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/u3EFQJr</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[LunaAtlas]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>.</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/sZGjZLC</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/tElJqxt.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>I kinda want to do this as well.</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/sZGjZLC</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[raftus]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>The shoe is on the other foot now.</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/aN0UZcG</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/ptbq0Jk.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/aN0UZcG</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[MrNobodyLivesHere]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>WW3 didn’t just “happen”</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/fLpHpOd</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/gG63ls7.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Liam Nissan one of the good ones. Terrible actor though.</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/fLp